  "description": "CHARTER: experiment variants + auto-publish gate dry-run evidence (edit distance, clean runs). Answers 'is the gate earning the right to auto-publish?'. Lab variant-experiment panels PARKED 2026-07-02 (git history): restore when the model-eval loop (poindexter#803 Plan 2) activates real experiments."
